Kapepula began to explain the heartbreaking story about the week he had suffered the loss of his girlfriend and how the tragedy motivated him CAPE TOWN - Wits wing Bin Kasende Kapepula gave an emotional post-match interview which you will not forget very easily  The 23-year-old was named the Player that Rocks after his side's 30-29 win over UCT in the Varsity Cup. He gave his post-match interview wearing a vest with the words "RIP Christine Osborne. I love you baby". Kapepula began to explain the heartbreaking story about the week he had suffered the loss of his girlfriend and how the tragedy motivated him.  (Edited by Shimoney Regter)